# <%= name %>

PCS project for managing private cloud infrastructure.

## Getting Started

```bash
# Create a site
pcs site add <name>

# Discover devices on the network
pcs device scan

# Configure a device
pcs device set <id> hostname=myhost type=pve

# Start a service
pcs service start dnsmasq

# Configure this host as control plane
pcs cp setup
```

## Project Structure

```
pcs.rb                      # Project configuration (loaded on boot)
data/roles.yml              # Device role definitions
sites/<site>/site.yml       # Site-specific network config
sites/<site>/hosts.yml      # Discovered hosts
```
